<h1>DRAFT - Civil Registration Authorities</h1>


 <p class="lead">This page provides you with a brief summary of various sources of information on the Civil Registration system for England and Wales; and it's records of Overseas events. It then moves onto summarising the Civil Registrations systems for Scotland, Northern Ireland and some of the United Kingdom's nearest neighbours: the Isle of Man, Ireland and the Channel Isles.</p>

